<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/login.css">
    <title>login</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container" id="container">
        <div class="form-container sign-up-container">
            <form action="newsletters.html">
                <h1>Créer un Compte</h1>
                <input type="matricule" placeholder="Matricule" />
                <input type="username" placeholder="Username" />
                <input type="password" placeholder="Password" />
                <button>S'inscrire</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="form-container sign-in-container">
            <form action="sidenav.html">
                <img src="./static/img/logo2.png" alt="">
                <h1>Se connecter</h1>
                <input type="username" placeholder="Username" />
                <input type="password" placeholder="Password" />
                <button>Se connecter</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div class="overlay-container">
            <div class="overlay">
                <div class="overlay-panel overlay-left">
                    <h1>Ah, te revoila!</h1>
                    <p>Cher etudiant de l'USTHB,<br>voici le meilleur moyen pour toi de trouver un stage rapidement !
                    </p>
                    <button class="ghost" id="signIn">Sign In</button>
                </div>
                <div class="overlay-panel overlay-right">
                    <h1>Salut !</h1>
                    <p>Tu n'as toujours pas de compte ?<br>Inscris-toi et assure-toi de ne rater aucune offre !</p>
                    <button class="ghost" id="signUp">Sign Up</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <script type="text/javascript" src="./static/js/login.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>

</html>